text: Ibragimovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starokurmashevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 128 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Kushnarenkovo, 13 km from Starokurmashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Ibragimovo, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
